{"tid":1812584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖）原來北韓都有大遊行…","createTime":"2020-01-05T15:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T15:30:04.000Z","uid":125168,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7064afa5f1cbca27f688fc826d30175fae855a76","tid":1812584,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T15:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bbkBGwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbkBGwz.jpg&h=5472c7fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大批民眾在平壤遊行表達忠於領袖金正恩<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】北韓有大批民眾遊行，表達對領袖金正恩的忠誠。<br />\n<br />\n數以萬計的民眾站滿平壤的金日成廣場，他們高叫勞動黨、國家和人民軍最高領袖金正恩萬歲的口號。勞動黨官員表示北韓要走的道路有很多困難，但在黨的領導下，加上擁有強而有力的武器，以及巨大的自主經濟，相信北韓必定會取得最後勝利。<br />\n<br />\n過往數年的遊行都是緊接在北韓領袖金正恩的元旦講話後，但今年沒有元旦講話，遊行改為支持勞動黨第七屆五中全會的會議成果。<br />\n<br />\n另外南韓總統文在寅將於星期二發表新年賀詞，韓聯社的分析認為，賀詞內容會以改善民生，和朝鮮半島和平兩大基調為主。"},{"pid":"e3ce2f5449de8559fd7c7257b74fb60a7494bfcd","tid":1812584,"uid":125168,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T15:06:39.000Z","msg":"而支那人想扮有遊行自由都無得扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80b33b3b8c2040cee582dd5e9589dddf507a973","tid":1812584,"uid":3122,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T15:07:52.000Z","msg":"多人到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc348b8bb4db23ca114360687c28bf5e926e4823","tid":1812584,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T15:07:54.000Z","msg":"細頸瓶幾時搞番個"},{"pid":"34f705f0224314229d622c80fb810ddb4c94b44b","tid":1812584,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a80b33b3b8c2040cee582dd5e9589dddf507a973","tid":1812584,"uid":3122,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T15:07:52.000Z","msg":"多人到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T15:08:24.000Z","msg":"唔去可能有生命危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" cla